It's a small aim-map i hope you like the way we created this map!
Terrors have AK, CT's m4. you have pistols, too ( usp + glock18 )

There is a little (secret area) if there is somebody afk... just try "swimming"

You can also shoot through the palms and crates!
By the way, there are 22 Spawn Points.
